Titolo: Of Orcs and Men

Anno: 2012

Descrizione: Of Orcs and Men is a fantasy action role-playing game developed by Cyanide and Spiders for PlayStation 3, Xbox 360 and PC. The Empire of Men's oppressive threat looms over the territories of the Orcs and the Goblins. Goblins are systematically persecuted and slaughtered, while Orcs not killed in battle are captured and enslaved.
Two prequels, titled Styx: Master of Shadows (2014) and Styx: Shards of Darkness (2017), came out with Styx the goblin as the main protagonist.

Genere: Non specificato


Valutazione: 63
